# DAO Governance Data Model

## Entities

### Entity: Member

A DAO participant with voting power.

```yaml
entity: Member
type: entity
properties:
  id:
    type: string
    required: true
  wallet:
    type: string
    required: true
  voting_power:
    type: number
    required: true
states: [active, delegated, suspended]
lifecycle: active → delegated → suspended
```

### Entity: Proposal

A governance item submitted for member voting.

```yaml
entity: Proposal
type: entity
properties:
  id:
    type: string
    required: true
  title:
    type: string
    required: true
  quorum_required:
    type: number
    required: true
  status:
    type: enum
    required: true
states: [draft, active, passed, rejected, executed]
lifecycle: draft → active → passed → executed
```

### Entity: Vote

A member decision on a proposal.

```yaml
entity: Vote
type: event
properties:
  member_id:
    type: string
    required: true
  proposal_id:
    type: string
    required: true
  choice:
    type: enum
    required: true
  weight:
    type: number
    required: true
states: [cast, counted]
lifecycle: cast → counted
```

### Entity: TreasuryAllocation

Funds allocated by an executed proposal.

```yaml
entity: TreasuryAllocation
type: entity
properties:
  id:
    type: string
    required: true
  proposal_id:
    type: string
    required: true
  amount:
    type: number
    required: true
  recipient:
    type: string
    required: true
states: [approved, executed, canceled]
lifecycle: approved → executed
```

## Relationships

### Relationship: Member → Proposal

```yaml
relationship: Member → Proposal
verb: submits
cardinality: 1:N
required: true
```

### Relationship: Member → Vote

```yaml
relationship: Member → Vote
verb: casts
cardinality: 1:N
required: true
```

### Relationship: Proposal → Vote

```yaml
relationship: Proposal → Vote
verb: receives
cardinality: 1:N
required: true
```

### Relationship: Proposal → TreasuryAllocation

```yaml
relationship: Proposal → TreasuryAllocation
verb: authorizes
cardinality: 1:1
required: false
```
